houses.desc: A nice family house on Vestergade in Aarhus. The noise in the area is at a minimum and there a park for the kids nearby. Nearest grocerystore is 10 min walk or 2 min. drive
2 bedrooms and a livingroom / Kitchen. perfect for 2 good friends to movie into. It got a dishwasher but washing facilities are in the basement and they are shared.
big house enough for 2 families, it has 3 bathrooms and 2 livingrooms. It got a wineceller and a big garden in the back with a small lake. Right now theres koi fish in it.
